=== Access ===
* From {{ill|lt=JR West|UNKNOWN|lt=JR}}{{ill|lt=Kusatsu Line|Q865516|WD=Q865516|1=Kusatsu Line}}{{ill|lt=Tehara Station|Q5362482|WD=Q5362482|1=Tehara Station}}, take the {{ill|lt=Kuri-chan Bus|Q11265638|WD=Q11265638|1=Kuri-chan Bus}} (Jitakinakatsu Line) and get off at Shimotoyama Miyagaya stop, then walk 3 minutes.
* 10 minutes by car from {{ill|lt=Meishin Expressway|Q904481|WD=Q904481|1=Meishin Expressway}}{{ill|lt=Ritto Interchange|Q11110683|WD=Q11110683|lt=Ritto IC|1=Ritto interchange}}.

=== Surroundings ===
* {{ill|lt=Shimotoyama Tumulus|Q60990033|WD=Q60990033|1=Shimotoyama Tumulus}} - Chieftain's tomb from the end of the 4th century to the beginning of the 5th century. A {{ill|lt=circular tomb|Q11394747|WD=Q11394747|1=Round Kofun}} with a diameter of 55 meters. Ritto City designated historic site.
* Jiyama Tumulus - A chieftain's tomb dating from the first half of the 5th century, second only to Shimotoyama Tumulus. {{ill|lt=scallop-shaped tumulus|Q11480883|WD=Q11480883|1=Scallop-shaped kofun}} with a length of 90 meters.

